<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[الضَّهل]</span>: الماء القليل، مثل الضَّحْل،<span class="c5"> والجميع:</span> ضُهُل.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فَعْلَة]</span>، بالهاء<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
